    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kaal Yoddha 是一款黑暗神话动作冒险游戏，你将扮演阿维安王子，一位技艺精湛的弓箭手兼战士，在被诅咒的岛屿上与恶魔战斗。精通弓箭、剑术和类魂系战斗，揭开远古面具的秘密，并在剧情驱动的黑暗奇幻世界中挑战残酷的 Boss！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320200/extras/f0d29fdcf6c20688141dd3325853f9ae.poster.avif?t=1770380140\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320200/extras/f0d29fdcf6c20688141dd3325853f9ae.webm?t=1770380140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>诅咒之岛，等待着你</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入《卡尔·约达》，这是一款以远古神话和被遗忘的传说为背景的单人黑暗奇幻动作冒险游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演阿维安王子，一位无畏的战士，被派往一座被诅咒的岛屿，恶魔势力利用被诅咒的远古面具散播腐化。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320200/extras/fbd4e5228ea7814e541ac2c95091dcaa.webp?t=1770380140\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320200/extras/fbd4e5228ea7814e541ac2c95091dcaa.poster.avif?t=1770380140\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=250 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >精准战斗——弓箭、剑、双斧</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验动态的类魂系战斗，把握时机、走位和精湛技艺至关重要。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用弓箭进行远程攻击。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >切换至剑术，进行激烈的近战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调整你的战斗风格，在无情的恶魔敌人面前生存下来。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >学习敌人的攻击模式，精准打击。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一场战斗都是对技巧的考验，而非运气。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320200/extras/9d9d6330c57dc508c8972050644981b4.poster.avif?t=1770380140\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320200/extras/9d9d6330c57dc508c8972050644981b4.webm?t=1770380140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >面具的诅咒</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这座岛屿被远古恶魔诞生的诅咒面具所笼罩</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索诡异的森林、残破的寺庙、隐秘的洞穴和摇摇欲坠的圣所，这是一个现实崩塌的地方，通过壁画、遗迹和神秘的笔记，揭开环境叙事的面纱。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320200/extras/c49ce90effd4466bf1f7a1cc55e66132.poster.avif?t=1770380140\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320200/extras/c49ce90effd4466bf1f7a1cc55e66132.webm?t=1770380140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>史诗级首领战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对高耸的怪物、受诅咒的战士和恶魔般的实体，它们都诞生于岛屿的腐化之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >胜利并非唾手可得，而是需要努力争取。你能否打破诅咒，重振家族荣耀，还是会被统治岛屿的黑暗吞噬？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拿起你的弓箭，拔出你的利刃，成为真正的战士。</strong></p>",
